@startuml

title Simple Backup Orchestrator Flow
autonumber

actor "Scheduler / Manual Trigger" as Trigger
participant "GitLab CI" as CI
participant "Runner (Docker)" as R
participant "Node A" as A
participant "Node B" as B
participant "Node C Host" as C
participant "GitLab Job Log" as JL
participant "Grafana / Loki" as G

Trigger -> CI: Trigger pipeline
CI -> R: Start backup job
R -> R: Evaluate BACKUP flags

par Node A
  R -> A: Run backup script via SSH
  A -> A: Backup + retention
  A --> R: Log output (stdout/json)
else Node B
  R -> B: Run local shell script
  B -> B: Backup + retention
  B --> R: Log output (stdout/json)
else Node C
  R -> C: SSH ke host yang sama
  C -> C: Backup + retention
  C --> R: Log output (stdout/json)
end

note over R,C
Runner berjalan di Docker,
Node C host ada di server yang sama.
Eksekusi tetap lewat SSH.
end note

alt Log ke GitLab job log
  R -> JL: Stream stdout
else Log terstruktur ke observability stack
  R -> G: Send json log
end
@enduml
